<title>USA: Xscribe names chief financial officer.</title>
<headline>Xscribe names chief financial officer.</headline>
<dateline>SAN DIEGO 1996-11-26</dateline>
<text>
<p>Xscribe Corp said Tuesday it named Peter Harker as chief financial officer, effective December 1.</p>
<p>Harker joined Xscribe in 1995 as corporate controller and replaces Bruce Myers who resigned as part of a broader restructuring. Xscribe recently sold its court-reporting products business to focus on its scanner business.</p>
<p>The company provides high-performance document and microfilm scanners and image capture systems to legal, financial, government, and commercial enterprises.</p>
